# Backend Environment Variables

## Required Variables

# MongoDB connection string
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster.mongodb.net/chainguard?retryWrites=true&w=majority

# Server port
PORT=5000

## Optional Variables (defaults provided)
NODE_ENV=production

## Notes
- MongoDB Atlas is recommended for cloud deployment
- Update MONGODB_URI with your actual connection string
- PORT can be any available port (5000 is default)
